#!/bin/bash

# change this line if you are creating a new env
source /home/ubuntu/anaconda3/bin/activate
which python
python --version

# install GDAL
sudo apt update
sudo apt install gdal-bin libgdal-dev -y

# Use cat to create the requirements.txt file
cat <<EOL > requirements.txt
